author: Xbox
description:
Nodding Heads Games announces Raji: Kaliyuga, the sequel to Raji: An Ancient Epic, set six years later. The unsealing of the heavens by the asura warlord Mahabalasura escalates the conflict within the game to a cosmic level. This grand battle encompasses not only mortals but also gods, asuras, and mystical entities.

Raji, now a seasoned warrior, and her dreamwalking brother Darsh, journey to the Eternal Summit to save or destroy the universe. Raji: Kaliyuga features dual protagonists: Raji, with acrobatic martial arts and the Trishul, and Darsh, with immense Siddhi powers that control gravity, time, and energy. It introduces customized evasion for Raji and a siddhi-yielding system for Darsh, allowing unique combat styles. 

The game shifts from an isometric action-adventure to a third-person action-adventure, with Nodding Heads Games committed to delivering a high-quality experience for fans.

Raji: Kaliyuga is coming to Xbox Series X|S and Xbox on PC as an Xbox Play Anywhere title a
title: Raji: Kaliyuga Official Reveal Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview 2025

author: Xbox
description:
CloverPit is available to play today with Xbox Series X|S, Xbox on PC, and Xbox Game Pass! 
CloverPit is the demonic lovechild of Balatro and Buckshot Roulette from Indie studio Panik Arcade (maker of the fan favorite Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom) and publisher Future Friends Games (The Cabin Factory, SUMMERHOUSE, Exo One). 

About the game:
CloverPit locks you in a rusty cell with a slot machine and an ATM, in which players must pay off their debt or fall to ruin – literally. Manipulate the slot machine to earn extra coins. Turn the odds in your favor with various prizes and charms that trigger big big combos, snowballing into a dazzling lucky run. Bend the rules, break the game, and pay off your debts!

Trailer by Franck Besançon
Music composed by Clement Panchout

CloverPIt is available on Xbox Series X|S and Xbox on PC as an Xbox Play Anywhere title.

author: Xbox
description:
Total Chaos is now haunting Xbox. 

Play it today on Xbox Series X|S and Xbox Game Pass - including Play Anywhere support for Console, PC, and Cloud.

Developed by Sam Prebble and published by Apogee Entertainment in partnership with Atari's Infogrames label, Total Chaos is a next-gen survival horror experience that began as one of the most celebrated DOOM II Custom WADs ever created... Now reborn as a standalone title built for modern platforms.

A grim descent into terror, Total Chaos blends eerie exploration, methodical melee combat, limited resources, and grotesque horror creatures into a mind-twisting journey across a forgotten coal mining colony called Fort Oasis. As your sanity slowly unravels, your only chance is to fight, scavenge, and uncover the island’s deadly secrets before they consume you whole.

• AVAILABLE TODAY on Xbox Series X|S + Xbox Game Pass
• Day One on Xbox Game Pass (Console / PC / Cloud)
• Xbox Play Anywhere support
• Features NEW original music by Silent Hi
title: Total Chaos - Console Launch Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview 2025
